  "detailed_description": "It's a first-person horror room escape game. You have to solve puzzles in a dark atmosphere, avoiding monitors. Never get caught.<br />\r\nIt's a place where you've been studying soul transfer for the rest of your life, and that's the wrong way to do it... \"Free me from the curse.\"<br />\r\nTo go up each floor, you must enter the correct ancient characters. You must find hidden keys and hints and open a box or safe.<br />\r\nThe hidden space is distorted. Take a close look at the wall.",
